data.description: Situated on expansive 1.09-acre lot, this cozy ranch-style home presents a unique opportunity to customize and renovate this charming property to your unique style and preferences. Offering endless possibilities, with 924 sq ft of living space, 2 bed, 1 bath and charming fireplace adds a touch of comfort to this property. Explore the potential of the full basement, partially finished and offering multiple uses such as additional living space, a workshop, recreational area, or storage, allowing you to tailor the space to suit your needs. The outdoors with ample space for expansion, gardening, outdoor activities and storage shed. Conveniently located close to essential amenities, schools, parks, Rtes 58 ,495 and 44. Don’t miss out on this exceptional opportunity to create your dream home. New 3 bed septic to be installed prior to close. No showings before open house on 4/6 12-2:00 pm
